OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FStuart has been sleeping in a tent by
OL,7,Fthe river while a weather warning
OL,8,Fdeclared an extraordinary risk to life.
OL,10,FHe is from South Africa but says the
OL,11,Fheat feels worse in Cardiff.
OL,13,F"The heat, I would say, is sometimes
OL,14,Fworse than the cold," he explained.
OL,16,F"The cold, they have a little bit more
OL,17,Fprovision, but the heat it feels like
OL,18,Fan afterthought."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
