OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FTen councils across Wales have told
OL,7,FITV News their Severe Weather
OL,8,FEmergency Protocol were activated, as
OL,9,FCardiff the UK record for the highest
OL,10,Fminimum temperature in June - where
OL,11,Fthe temperature only went down to
OL,12,F23.5C overnight at Bute Park.
OL,14,FThose councils are providing emergency
OL,15,Faccommodation and extra support, such
OL,16,Fas water and sun cream for rough
OL,17,Fsleepers.
OL,19,FBut providing support is not
OL,20,Fcompulsory for local authorities
OL,21,Fduring the extreme heat.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
