PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FStuart said: "You can just bake like
OL,7,Fan oven in the little tent, and that's
OL,8,Fjust unhealthy and pretty dangerous,
OL,9,Freally."
OL,11,FCharities like The Wallich are trying
OL,12,Fto bridge the gap, providing a cool
OL,13,Fplace to spend time during the day
OL,14,Fwhen temperatures are at their highest.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
