SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FInterim CEO Sian Aldridge said: "The
OL,7,Fneeds are different in this warm
OL,8,Fweather. Severe Weather Emergency
OL,9,FProtocol often provides extra support
OL,10,Fand accommodation overnight, but we
OL,11,Freally need to see spaces opened up so
OL,12,Fpeople can get that respite away from
OL,13,Fthe sun, reduce harm and obviously
OL,14,Freduce risk to life."
OL,16,FOsian, who was formerly homeless, now
OL,17,Fvolunteers at The Wallich to give back
OL,18,Fto the place that helped him.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
