PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FHe said: "It's a real situation where
OL,7,Fit's life or death. It's not just an
OL,8,Finconvenience.
OL,10,F"In the summer, in the heat, people
OL,11,Fhave fun, people have drinks, people
OL,12,Fgo and see friends.
OL,14,F"But when it comes to the people on
OL,15,Fthe streets, they have no option but
OL,16,Fto just sit there, find respite, find
OL,17,Fshade.
OL,19,F"And they're very lucky to get some
OL,20,Fwater, very lucky to get any
OL,21,Facknowledgement really."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
