CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FOsian said The Wallich do not just
OL,7,Fprovide shade and water, but also
OL,8,Fsomeone to talk to.
OL,10,FHe said: "It's so scary and
OL,11,Fintimidating to open up to people,
OL,12,Fwhereas at The Wallich it's so easy to
OL,13,Fbe upfront and honest because people
OL,14,Fcare and people want to support you."
OL,16,FAs well as their Solutions Centre, The
OL,17,FWallich outreach teams also provide
OL,18,Fwater, suncream, hats, and build
OL,19,Frelationships to encourage people into
OL,20,Fsupport services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
