CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FSian Aldridge said: "They really are
OL,7,Fvulnerable to the heat.
OL,9,F"We as a community need to reach out
OL,10,Fand support people.
OL,12,F"If you see someone struggling, please
OL,13,Fask if you can help, offer them water
OL,14,For a cold drink. If you are really
OL,15,Fconcerned, please call the emergency
OL,16,Fservices."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
