OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FThe Wallich said there has been a rise
OL,7,Fof around 30% in curbside living,
OL,8,Fmeaning people living in cars or vans,
OL,9,Fwhich are even more of a risk in the
OL,10,Fheat.
OL,12,FSian added: "It's so difficult for
OL,13,Fpeople; they can't escape it. It's
OL,14,Frelentless."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
