OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,FA Cardiff Council spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our Homelessness and Specialist
OL,8,FHousing teams have taken a number of
OL,9,Fproactive steps to support people
OL,10,Fsleeping rough and other vulnerable
OL,11,Fresidents during the extreme heat,
OL,12,Fincluding sharing Public Health Wales
OL,13,Fguidance to help people understand the
OL,14,Frisks associated with the high
OL,15,Ftemperatures and how to stay safe.
OL,17,F"Additional staff have been brought in
OL,18,Fto strengthen this response, and we
OL,19,Fare working closely with partners to
OL,20,Fprovide co-ordinated support.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
