PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782499685
OL,3,C'It's life or death': Homeless in the
OL,4,Cextreme heat
OL,6,F"Additional accommodation has been
OL,7,Fmade available to ensure people have
OL,8,Faccess to safe shelter during the
OL,9,Fhottest periods.
OL,11,F"Teams are also carrying out enhanced
OL,12,Fwelfare checks, with a particular
OL,13,Ffocus on those most at risk, including
OL,14,Fpeople sleeping rough, those with
OL,15,Funderlying health conditions and older
OL,16,Fresidents.
OL,18,F"Practical support is being provided,
OL,19,Fincluding access to drinking water,
OL,20,Fsun protection and appropriate
OL,21,Fclothing where needed."
OL,26,@nD@AOU}D@WO]
